Comment: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,/ FIRST FRAME OF ED /
Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.73,0:00:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A contenção se desintegrou.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.07,0:00:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Não há leituras de presença de Gauna.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.48,0:00:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Qual é o status da cimera?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.35,0:00:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Cimera Tsumugi foi confirmada viva.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.65,0:00:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gauna realmente foram cruéis.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.35,0:00:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não permitirei que eles façam isso com meus amigos.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.50,0:00:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A densidade de partículas Heigus em Tsumugi aumentou\Ndetetada.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.20,0:00:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pare essa loucura, Tsumugi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.24,0:00:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi, escute-nos!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.79,0:00:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinatose, danos pesados!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.20,0:00:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A densidade de partículas Heigus no G550\Nestá aumentando drasticamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.46,0:00:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Merda!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.05,0:00:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sidonia!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.34,0:00:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,O feixe foi desviado\Nao atingir Tsumugi e Shinatose.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.53,0:00:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Alguém...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.08,0:00:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Ajuda a Tsumugi...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.60,0:00:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Tsumugi...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.31,0:00:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Tsumugi é—
