Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Há muitos.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.43,0:06:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela parece um pouco melhor agora.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.44,0:07:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,O tubo do reator 1024 será\Nlimpado conforme programado.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.40,0:07:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}A limpeza vai...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Quero agradecer Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouvi que atualizaram o menu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos tentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu passo.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Nagate...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.06,0:07:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A nave-colônia enviou uma vanguarda e \Ffoi atacada no retorno para Sidonia, certo?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.36,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou aliviado que pelo menos algumas pessoas \Fchegaram ao Planeta Sete.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.20,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas a colmeia grande está \Faproximando do sistema estelar Lem.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A comida estava boa.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é tudo o que você está comendo?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.58,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Boa noite.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Boa noite.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele vai ficar bem?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.55,0:08:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele parece muito cansado.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Me maravilho se ele está dormindo bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.98,0:08:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que Tanikaze{**-san} nunca diria a ninguém se estivesse cansado ou não se sentisse bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Essa atitude tem seus encantos.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.69,0:08:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas também me preocupa.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.45,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu conhecia alguém faz tempo\Nque era muito semelhante a Nagate.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.70,0:08:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Às vezes fico ansioso quando vejo ele\Ntentando carregar todo o mundo nas costas.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas tenho certeza de que ele ficará bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele se animará se você\Nlhe der um tempinho sozinho.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze Nagate[T0].
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.36,0:09:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Você veio visitar Tsumugi novamente?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.07,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,E olá.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.58,0:09:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi foi transferida para o contêiner padrão.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sua placenta já se regenerou quase completamente,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,então só é questão de tempo até ela recuperar a consciência.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,De fato?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.57,0:10:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela se moveu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Puta que pariu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.21,0:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela se moveu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é falta de educação, Nagate.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.24,0:10:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshijiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0].
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.09,0:10:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Hoshijiro...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.34,0:11:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0].
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.36,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.37,0:11:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Quando eu adormeci?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Você parecia bem feliz dormindo.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.05,0:11:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Acordou!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-Tanikaze[T0]?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou tão feliz!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.65,0:11:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana[T0]!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está bem!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado a você.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.49,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Graças a Deus.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.16,0:12:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu trouxe esse cara quando soube que você chegou.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.79,0:12:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,O gato!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Posso tocar nele?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.75,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Seja suave.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.75,0:12:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.96,0:12:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,É tão fofo e macio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:32.01,100 Sights,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}100 Atrações de Sidonia
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:29.01,100 Sights - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Automático Restaurante
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:32.01,100 Sights - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Ponte da Parede Externa, Caminho Interno
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.32,0:12:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,O grande agrupamento de colmeias na verdade se encontra\No lado oposto do estrela Lem.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele não pode nos perceber na sombra da estrela.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.57,0:12:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sidonia irá desacelerar para entrar no sistema estelar conforme programado.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Seja cauteloso.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,E a criatura chifruda?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.25,0:13:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela se recuperou completamente e está em standby\Nosso quarto fora do núcleo armadurado de Sidonia.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Muito bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.97,0:13:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mesmo com Tsumugi, não temos a menor chance contra o grande ninho coletivo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.44,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A capitã tem alguma surpresa na manga?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.23,0:13:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Diante da última batalha, o grupo contrário à cimera perdeu bastante força.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Como se esperava.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,E a questão restante?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.58,0:13:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Logo será submetida a testes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.96,0:13:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmite minha confiança nela ao Dr. Yure.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Como desejar.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.22,0:13:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, dá para ver as estrelas aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.43,0:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que este quarto é um pouco maior do que o último também.
