Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.39,0:21:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare de se zombar de mim, Avó.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpe.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.90,0:21:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu só fico aliviada em ver que você está bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.44,0:21:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu estava um pouco preocupada porque você estava levando muito tempo para se recuperar.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.45,0:21:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Devemos ajustar também a sua perna artificial.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Aguarde.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou recebendo outra chamada.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.91,0:21:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem, vou atender.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.46,0:21:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Até logo, vovó.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.21,0:22:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.17,0:22:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.09,0:22:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.80,0:22:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Peço desculpas pela falta de aviso, mas...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.43,0:22:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Bem, um...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Posso ficar na sua casa hoje à noite?
