Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:36.25,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se este mundo está condenado à destruição,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:36.25,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se esta era é condenada ao caos,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:39.79,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se minha vida está em perigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:39.79,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se meu destino está selado,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:45.38,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então por que eu devo viver?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:45.38,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o que devo crer para viver?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:51.05,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,1. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se não tivesse conhecido você,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:51.05,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,2. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então nunca teria sentido esta dor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:54.47,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,3. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}que me arranca o coração
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:54.47,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,4. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}nunca havia sentido uma dor assim
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:23:01.06,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,5. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}É um enterro primitivo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:23:01.06,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,6. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}No horizonte do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:03.82,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]It is a crude requiem
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:03.82,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]sora no kanata
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:05.28,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ecoando para
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:05.28,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}narisou foi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:09.11,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}as alturas do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:09.11,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}infindável requeim
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:11.03,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}E até agora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:11.03,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]sore demo mada
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:12.74,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}neste mundo sem sentido
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:12.74,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}buscando
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:16.16,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Eu busco
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:16.16,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}diferente do agora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.12,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}por ti
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.12,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o que te dizia
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:21.79,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Eu me lembro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:21.79,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}também da alegria de nos encontrarmos
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.79,0:23:25.50,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e até mesmo do calor do abraço
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.79,0:23:25.50,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}a frieza da distância
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:29.72,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e a passagem do seu being
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:29.72,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu nome eu lembro todo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:32.80,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}porque te amei
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:32.80,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}amai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:36.56,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Gelo cresce no meu coração
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:36.56,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}cartas que me acompanham também
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:40.27,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}sobre as feridas dentro de mim
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:40.27,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}também restam marcas nas minhas feridas
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:44.61,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,1. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Eu levarei tudo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:44.61,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,2. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e caminharei pelo meu caminho
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:51.66,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,3. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e caminharei pelo meu caminho
